        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7263",
        "content": "Hard had been their trouble before, but it was child's play to what they met in seeking the comb. Win it they did, and the Boar Truith they hunted into the deep sea, and it was never known whither he went.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
